---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro"
import Header from "@/components/Header.astro"
import Footer from "@/components/Footer.astro"
import HeroSection from "@/components/HeroSection.astro"
---

<Layout title="Mais - Bruno Pulis">
	<Header />
	<main>
		<HeroSection
			title="Mais"
			description="Uma grande lista de todas as páginas, projetos, posts no meu site."
		/>
		<section class="bg-white py-16 dark:bg-gray-800">
			<div class="container px-5 mx-auto">
				<div class="mb-24 grid items-center gap-12 md:grid-cols-1">
					<div>
						<h2 class="mb-6 text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
							Lista das páginas
						</h2>
						<p class="mb-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
							Essa é minha <span lang="en">slash page</span>, você pode encontrar todos os tipos em <a class="hover:offset font-bold text-red-950 hover:underline hover:underline-offset-8" href="https://slashpages.net/">slashes pages</a>
						</p>

						<ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 ml-6 space-y-2">
              <li class="mb-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300"><a class="hover:offset font-bold text-[20px] text-red-950 hover:underline hover:underline-offset-8" href="/blogroll">/blogroll</a>: Blogs que eu sigo e recomendo;</li>
							<!-- <li class="mb-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300"><a class="hover:offset font-bold text-[20px] text-red-950 hover:underline hover:underline-offset-8" href="/bookmarks">/bookmarks</a>: Meus links favoritos</li> -->
							<li class="mb-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300"><a class="hover:offset font-bold text-[20px] text-red-950 hover:underline hover:underline-offset-8" href="/bookshelf">/reading</a>: Os livros que li desde 2018.</li>
							<li class="mb-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300"><a class="hover:offset font-bold text-[20px] text-red-950 hover:underline hover:underline-offset-8" href="/colophon">/colophon</a>: uma página que descreve como o site foi feito</li>
              <li class="mb-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300"><a class="hover:offset font-bold text-[20px] text-red-950 hover:underline hover:underline-offset-8" href="/guestbook">/guestbook</a>: Meu livro de visitas que você pode assinar!</li>
              <li class="mb-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300"><a class="hover:offset font-bold text-[20px] text-red-950 hover:underline hover:underline-offset-8" href="/ai">/ai</a>: Como utiliza inteligência artificial no meu site.</li>
							<li class="mb-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300"><a class="hover:offset font-bold text-[20px] text-red-950 hover:underline hover:underline-offset-8" href="/notes">/notes</a>: Minhas notas curtas.</li>
							<li class="mb-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300"><a class="hover:offset font-bold text-[20px] text-red-950 hover:underline hover:underline-offset-8" href="/now">/now</a>: Coisas que estou fazendo agora.</li>
							<li class="mb-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300"><a class="hover:offset font-bold text-[20px] text-red-950 hover:underline hover:underline-offset-8" href="/referrals">/referrals</a>: Meus links de afiliado.</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
	<Footer />
</Layout>
